title: Counter-Strike Source Extreme MapPack v2
description:
Pack contains over 1000+ maps. All maps work perfect (without texture/models/sounds and any other problem) and have mini-map on radar position.

To install on steam:
- install/unpack all files to your game dir (something like: D:/Games/Steam/SteamApps/common/Counter-Strike Source/ - where placed hl2.exe).

To install on no-steam:
- install/unpack all files to your game dir (something like: D:/Games/Counter-Strike Source/ - where placed hl2.exe).
